trans-unit.source: Represents a collection of binding parameters that store information used by binding elements to build factories.
trans-unit.target: 表示繫結參數的集合，這些參數可儲存繫結項目建立處理站時所用的資訊。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.BindingParameterCollection> is a collection of objects that is used when a custom binding needs to provide additional parameters to another binding.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.BindingParameterCollection> 是物件的集合，當自訂繫結需要提供其他參數給另一個繫結時，會使用此集合。

trans-unit.source: For example, the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.SecurityBindingElement> looks for <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ServiceSecurityAuditBehavior> in the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.BindingParameterCollection> to determine Security auditing settings.
trans-unit.target: 例如，<xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.SecurityBindingElement> 會在 <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ServiceSecurityAuditBehavior> 中尋找 <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.BindingParameterCollection>，以判斷安全性稽核設定。

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.Channels.BindingParameterCollection" /> class.
trans-unit.target: 初始化 <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.Channels.BindingParameterCollection" /> 類別的新執行個體。
